  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for investor education in climate infrastructure&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Aligned Intermediary&#x2019;s mission is to accelerate and create the flow of private capital from long-term investors into climate infrastructure, enabling an energy transition and avoiding the worst impacts of climate change. This grant will fund the Intermediary&#x2019;s work to educate long-term investors and the public with investor materials, lessons learned, and successes based on their model. The purpose of educating investors is to catalyze the larger long-term investor community to participate in the climate infrastructure sector. This grant will also fund the organization to support the research and development of an innovative, global Aligned Capital Climate Vehicle, focused on supporting climate infrastructure investments in emerging markets. The Intermediary&#x2019;s focus on climate infrastructure includes clean energy, water, and waste-to-value projects. &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
